data.description: Spacious and beautiful 5 bedroom, 4 bath home nestled at the end of the cul-de-sac in Sunrise Terrace. Featuring vaulted ceilings throughout and all the natural lighting you need, this property is boasting a huge master suite with private bath and walk-in closet, nicely appointed kitchen with center island and family room complete with a gas fireplace. Finished basement includes more room to roam and a full bath. Good sized back yard, large deck, 2 car attached garage and more located only minutes from Big Johnson Reservoir and a short distance to military bases.
